<script>
function runPythonCode() {
    var codeCell = document.createElement('code');
    codeCell.innerText = `
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

x = np.linspace(0, 10, 100)
y = np.sin(x)

plt.plot(x, y)
plt.xlabel('x')
plt.ylabel('y')
plt.title('Sine Wave')
plt.grid(True)
plt.savefig('sine_wave.png')
plt.show()
    `;
    document.body.appendChild(codeCell);
    window.eval(codeCell.innerText);
}
</script>
